1) Most modern CLIs have a way to open a new tab or window.

    Find out a way to open a new tab and window. Bonus points for working out the keyboard shortcuts for doing so.

2) Can you think of any reasons why we might use the `echo` command? Why so?

3) Type in `echo "Hello, world`. What do you get? If you are not sure how to exit out of this state, stop here and I will cover how to overcome such issues in brief.